name: Pedukuhan karang buncing carangsari
address: Jl tukad panet No.4, Carangsari, Kec. Petang, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80353, Indonesia
review 1:
I had the most incredible experience staying at this unique jungle accommodation nestled within an expansive temple complex in Bali. From the moment I arrived, I was immersed in the beauty of nature and surrounded by lush greenery. Waking up to the sounds of birds and the rustling leaves was a surreal experience that left me in awe. The room was impeccably clean. And oh, the private pool! It was an absolute dream. I had my own oasis of tranquility where I could unwind and soak in the natural beauty that surrounded me. Whether taking a refreshing dip during the day or gazing at the starlit sky at night, it was an experience like no other.

The staffâ€™s warm hospitality made my stay even more special. They ensured my comfort all the time. Whether with a great massage or the local flavors and international cuisine in the meals provided.

A must-visit!!!
review 2: Magnificent place overlooking the jungle valley, truly wonderful experience. Food is made with so much love and the services is outstanding!
review 3: This place is surrounded by greenery but very ill maintained. There are giant spiders in the room and cockroaches on the bed. The owner frengky is rude, hostile and ill mannered. Do a favour on yourself and don't spoil your holidays by staying at this place. AVOID!!
review 4: Great ambience,and the dogs..they're super cute..
review 5: The owner is extremely friendly and nice to chat with.
